cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.LO. 

The paper discusses a method for improving software verification using machine learning techniques to predict the most appropriate SMT solver for a given proof obligation. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of machine learning also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the evaluation of different algorithms falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
